data.description: Welcome to Chateau Waikiki's coveted 1-bed, 1-bath unit, a perfect blend of island elegance and modern comfort. It boasts stylish tile and vinyl flooring, a space-efficient murphy bed, and a tranquil private lanai. The unit features an in-unit washer/dryer, central AC, and robust security with 24/7 guards, secure entry, and covered parking. A bonus storage locker adds to the practical design. Maintenance fees cover electricity, water, and sewer, simplifying your living experience. Enjoy premium amenities including fitness rooms, a meeting area, a swimming pool, BBQ facilities, and a unique workshop for residents. Located near the scenic Hilton Lagoon and Beaches, you're in a vibrant neighborhood with top-tier dining, lively nightlife, and diverse entertainment. This exceptional opportunity includes a potential VA loan assumption at a favorable 3.25%. Chateau Waikiki offers a lifestyle of convenience, security, and luxury. Embrace the chance to own a piece of paradise in one of Waikiki's most desirable areas.
